<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Profile Update Required</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7fa;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9800 0%, #f57c00 100%);
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .header .icon {
      font-size: 64px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
      color: #333333;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .alert-box {
      background-color: #fff3e0;
      border-left: 4px solid #ff9800;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }

    .reason-box {
      background-color: #ffebee;
      border: 2px solid #ef5350;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .reason-box h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #c62828;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9800 0%, #f57c00 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 15px 40px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 25px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }

    .button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .action-steps {
      background-color: #f0f7ff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }

    .action-steps h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #1976d2;
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .action-steps ol {
      margin: 15px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
    }

    .action-steps li {
      margin: 10px 0;
      color: #555;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #666666;
      font-size: 13px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #ff9800;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: #ff9800;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="icon">‚ö†Ô∏è</div>
      <h1>Profile Update Required</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="alert-box">
        <p style="margin:0; font-size: 16px;">
          <strong>Hi {{name}},</strong>
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">
          Your candidate profile requires some updates before it can be approved.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>
        Our review team has identified some issues that need to be addressed. Please review the feedback below and
        update your profile accordingly.
      </p>

      {{#if reason}}
      <div class="reason-box">
        <h3>üìù Feedback from Review Team:</h3>
        <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; line-height: 1.6;">{{reason}}</p>
      </div>
      {{/if}}

      <div class="action-steps">
        <h3>‚úÖ What You Need to Do:</h3>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Log in</strong> to your candidate portal</li>
          <li><strong>Review the feedback</strong> provided above carefully</li>
          <li><strong>Update your profile</strong> with the necessary corrections</li>
          <li><strong>Submit for re-review</strong> - our team will review it promptly</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{profileUrl}}" class="button">Update Your Profile</a>
      </div>

      <div style="background-color: #e3f2fd; border-left: 4px solid #2196f3; padding: 15px; margin: 25px 0; border-radius: 5px;">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px;">
          <strong>üí° Tip:</strong> Make sure all required fields are filled out completely and accurately. High-quality
          photos and detailed descriptions increase your chances of approval.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
        If you have any questions about the feedback or need assistance with your profile, please don't hesitate to
        contact our support team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #ff9800;">{{supportEmail}}</a>.
      </p>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #999; font-size: 13px;">
        Best regards,<br>
        <strong>The ITFY E-Voting Team</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated email from <strong>ITFY E-Voting Platform</strong></p>
      <p>
        <a href="{{profileUrl}}">Candidate Portal</a> |
        <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">Contact Support</a>
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 15px; color: #999;">
        ¬© {{formatDate currentYear}} ITFY E-Voting. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
